      <h3 class="step-title">Understanding.</h3>
      <p class="step-description">Starting from a clear beginning, we let the whole team to clarify doubts about the problem, customer, business, users, value proposition, and how successfully the solution could be.
 </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="step" id="definition">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="step-number">2</span>
      <h3 class="step-title">Definition.</h3>
      <p class="step-description">Helping to build a shared comprenhension among stakeholders, the entire team is encouraged to live a collaborative design session to define how the solution should be built.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="step" id="design">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="step-number">3</span>
      <h3 class="step-title">Design & Prototyping.</h3>
      <p class="step-description">We look to create a non-functional prototype as fast as possible and move forward into coding. Additionally we will suggest a User Research session to be considered in order to learn more about the product before launching it to the masses.
 </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="step" id="build">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="step-number">4</span>
      <h3 class="step-title">Build.</h3>
      <p class="step-description">The product should be coded at some point! We commit ourselves to constantly notify and show you all the progress along this module showing a working and functional product.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="step" id="measure">
